commit.message:
Use AC_CHECK_FUNCS to check for malloc, realloc

The previous checks for malloc/realloc fail during cross-compilation.
This seems to be a common issue¹²³. There are other workarounds, but
this seems to be the best approach since it retains the checks.

¹ https://sourceforge.net/p/mingw-w64/mailman/message/36424004/
² https://stackoverflow.com/q/9229079/4410590
³ https://stackoverflow.com/q/67116092/4410590
